  "tcmTraditionalUsage": {
    "en": "This preparation is made from the roots of Rhodiola, a plant that grows high in the mountains of Tibet. Neutral in nature, it helps to tonify and promote circulation. Rhodiola replenishes energy and promotes the oxygen-carrying capacity of the blood, making it useful for treating fatigue and preventing high altitude sickness.\n",
    "zh-Hant": "紅景天藥味甘、微苦，藥性微涼，能補氣養陰，強心益智，一般用於心力衰弱、體虛乏力、頭昏健忘等症。\n",
    "zh-Hans": "紅景天药味甘、微苦，药性微涼，能补气养阴，强心益智，一般用于心力衰弱、体虚乏力、头昏健忘等症。\n"
  },
  "tcmModernResearch": {
    "en": "Used for the prevention of acute mountain sickness.\n",
